Name: Undocking
checklistText:
<size=24>UNDOCKING</size>

1. OAMS PWR 			- ON
2. OAMS Valve 			- OPEN
3. Encoder CMD: 220 		- UNDOCK
4. Within 30 seconds, back away from target vehicle.

<size=20>EMERGENCY RELEASE</size>
1. EMER REL 			- PUSH
Note: Destroys the hooks on Gemini Spacecraft. Unable to dock after this.
